al/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfbdfa6558e92f69575b1ebb1a0275dbf70a4cc4","tid":752213,"uid":175056,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T15:58:42.000Z","msg":"小弟做IT  經常用電子產品<br />\n其實電子用品 用多左<br />\n會缺乏自我思考 更甚係社交能力<br />\n好多時候 係有錢人做成既一個現象<br />\n佢地由教育入手 感樣佢地可以保障自己仔女<br />\n令更少下一代向上發展 突圍而出<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n所以我一日都係用4個鐘電腦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其他時間見客/睇文件/書<br />\n<br />\n樓主 講得幾好 加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49f0e79e86570ffdf55ce4048587128739eba932","tid":752213,"uid":101154,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"bfbdfa6558e92f69575b1ebb1a0275dbf70a4cc4","tid":752213,"uid":175056,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T15:58:42.000Z","msg":"小弟做IT  經常用電子產品<br />\n其實電子用品 用多左<br />\n會缺乏自我思考 更甚係社交能力<br />\n好多時候 係有錢人做成既一個現象<br />\n佢地由教育入手 感樣佢地可以保障自己仔女<br />\n令更少下一代向上發展 突圍而出<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n所以我一日都係用4個鐘電腦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其他時間見客/睇文件/書<br />\n<br />\n樓主 講得幾好 加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T16:04:32.000Z","msg":"多謝巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n可惜個po沉左底"},{"pid":"0a2f1a504252fe1b62c9bdbced2a745a1f7f4ce6","tid":752213,"uid":171265,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T16:07:53.000Z","msg":"開po時間唔啱姐<br />\nPish<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5dcf146235bc30a7c1a1732dbb56581818fbed1a","tid":752213,"uid":101154,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"0a2f1a504252fe1b62c9bdbced2a745a1f7f4ce6","tid":752213,"uid":171265,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T16:07:53.000Z","msg":"開po時間唔啱姐<br />\nPish<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" cl